name: "The End" European Deer Mount Eight Point Buck Skull Sculpture Heavy
description:
Euro Mount Deer Sculpture
Handmade and welded entirely from metal, this one-of-a-kind Euro Mount Deer Sculpture is a unique piece of art, handcrafted for an exclusive experience.

Organic Feel
Any hunter or nature lover will admire this life-like deer skull and rack.
Made from repurposed steel, it's hard to tell that the entire piece is made of metal at first glance.
Durable Quality
Extremely durable with a clear polyurethane finish and rust-resistance.
Lasting longevity with a smooth, lasting shine.
Handcrafted proudly in the USA.
Product Details
Life-size Euro Mount Deer Rack design
Overall width: 27 inches
Weight: 9 pounds
